=head1 DESCRIPTION

A description of the stream's edge configuration that will be used to
sync with the Edge Agent IoT Greengrass component. The Edge Agent
component will run on an IoT Hub Device setup at your premise.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 DeletionConfig => L<Paws::KinesisVideo::DeletionConfig>

The deletion configuration is made up of the retention time
(C<EdgeRetentionInHours>) and local size configuration
(C<LocalSizeConfig>) details that are used to make the deletion.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> HubDeviceArn => Str

The "B<Internet of Things (IoT) Thing>" Arn of the stream.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> RecorderConfig => L<Paws::KinesisVideo::RecorderConfig>

The recorder configuration consists of the local C<MediaSourceConfig>
details, that are used as credentials to access the local media files
streamed on the camera.


=head2 UploaderConfig => L<Paws::KinesisVideo::UploaderConfig>

The uploader configuration contains the C<ScheduleExpression> details
that are used to schedule upload jobs for the recorded media files from
the Edge Agent to a Kinesis Video Stream.



